\newlabel{fig:fig3-ablations}{{9}{12}{Switching curves varying model capacity (left) and training duration (right) on the 2D Gaussian mixture. Larger/longer-trained models memorize better, confirming that generalization is a consequence of limited expressiveness.\relax }{figure.caption.9}{}}
